---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageTitle from '../components/PageTitle.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Quality Assurance | Peptide Shop" 
  description="Our commitment to purity. Learn about our HPLC and Mass Spectrometry testing protocols for research peptides."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "Quality Assurance", url: "/quality" }
  ]}
>
  
  <PageTitle 
    title="Quality Assurance"
    subtitle="In scientific research, data integrity depends on reagent integrity. We implement rigorous quality control to ensure every vial meets the highest standards."
    breadcrumbs={[
      { name: "Home", url: "/" },
      { name: "Quality" }
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Main Content Section -->
  <section style="padding: 80px 0; background: white;">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Testing Methods -->
      <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05), rgba(0, 150, 199, 0.05)); border-radius: 10px; padding: 40px; height: 100%; border: 2px solid rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.15);">
            <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077b6, #023e8a); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                <polyline points="7.5 4.21 12 6.81 16.5 4.21"></polyline>
                <polyline points="7.5 19.79 7.5 14.6 3 12"></polyline>
                <polyline points="21 12 16.5 14.6 16.5 19.79"></polyline>
                <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                <line x1="12" x2="12" y1="22.08" y2="12"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.5rem;">HPLC Analysis</h3>
            <p style="color: #64748b; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
              High-Performance Liquid Chromatography (HPLC) determines peptide purity. We guarantee minimum 99% purity for all catalog items, ensuring impurities like deletion sequences or incomplete synthesis byproducts are minimized.
            </p>
            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px;">
              <div style="display: flex; justify-content: between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                <span style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Purity Standard</span>
                <span style="color: #0077b6; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px;">≥99%</span>
              </div>
              <div style="background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.1); height: 8px; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;">
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0077b6, #023e8a); width: 99%; height: 100%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05), rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.05)); border-radius: 10px; padding: 40px; height: 100%; border: 2px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);">
            <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.5rem;">Mass Spectrometry</h3>
            <p style="color: #64748b; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
              Mass Spectrometry (MS) verifies molecular weight and peptide identity. This confirms the amino acid sequence is correct and matches the theoretical mass.
            </p>
            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px;">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <div style="color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 2px;">Molecular Confirmation</div>
                  <div style="color: #10b981; font-weight: 700;">100% Verified</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Certificate of Analysis -->
      <div class="row mb-5">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 50px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
            <h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 2rem;">
              Certificate of Analysis (COA)
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px;">
              Transparency is key. A Certificate of Analysis is available for every batch we produce. Download the COA directly from the product page before purchase.
            </p>

            <div class="row g-3">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Batch Number</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Date of Analysis</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Molecular Weight</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">HPLC Chromatogram</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Physical Appearance</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; padding: 16px; background: rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.05); border-radius: 10px;">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2" style="flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                  <span style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Solubility Profile</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Storage & Handling -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1), rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1)); border-radius: 10px; padding: 40px; border: 2px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);">
            <h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 1.75rem;">
              Storage & Handling
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 32px;">
              To maintain peptide quality after delivery, we recommend the following:
            </p>
            <div class="row g-4">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px;">
                  <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <path d="M3 9h18v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9Z"></path>
                    <path d="m3 9 2.45-4.9A2 2 0 0 1 7.24 3h9.52a2 2 0 0 1 1.8 1.1L21 9"></path>
                    <path d="M12 3v6"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h4 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.125rem;">Lyophilized Storage</h4>
                  <p style="color: #64748b; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">Store at -20°C immediately upon receipt</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px;">
                  <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                    <path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h4 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.125rem;">Light Protection</h4>
                  <p style="color: #64748b; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">Keep away from direct sunlight at all times</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div style="background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 24px;">
                  <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <path d="M8 2v4"></path>
                    <path d="M16 2v4"></path>
                    <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect>
                    <path d="M3 10h18"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <h4 style="color: #1e293b; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.125rem;">Freeze-Thaw Cycles</h4>
                  <p style="color: #64748b; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">Minimize cycles to preserve peptide integrity</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
